+ kindofbrown@users.sourceforge.net
-------------------------------------------

1. What is this?
  Simple bindings for OpenGL API.

2. How to install
  > make -f macosx_32.mk

  dig .konoha/gl directory at your launcing directory.
if you checkout svn repository, its easy to make symlink
from your $(homedir),

  > ln -s $(svn-package-checkoutdir) ~/.konoha

3. How to Use?
  For detailed build and API reference, see the project
web site:
    
          http://konoha.sourceforge.jp/wiki

  For quickly use, check out sample files.

  > konoha sample/gl_3.k

4. Bugs
  report is always welcome.

  kindofbrown@users.sourceforge.jp


